title: Looking for a Gold or Higher Team for Ranked 5's
body: Hi I'm looking for a Gold+ group of awesome guys/girls to play ranked 5's with, i am 21, i main Mid, Top and Jungle, but am proficient in all roles, i am only available to play between 5:30pm and 12pm as i work all day during the week as for weekends it depends if i have anything planned reply or add me if Ur interested.

replies.body: hey, we have a ranked team that needs a jungler/shotcaller. if you're keen hit me up in game
Why do you want to join a ranked team?
im looking to get better in team play and become more competitive also looking for a bigger challenge
